@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dslgdz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = 0.60
    v0 = wp.sin((v0 * (v1 + 0.27 * v0 + 0.73)))
    v1 = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.49 + v2 + 0.44) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.05)))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.47 - v0 + 0.03)) + ((v1 + 0.17 - v1 + 0.51) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.05)))
    v2 = 0.42
    v2 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.04 * v2 + 0.27)) + (wp.sin(v2 + 0.89) + (tmp + 0.69 / v0 + 0.58)))
    data[tid] = v0
